room_title: Escape room "The Study" by Mission: Escape Atlanta in Atlanta
room_address: 500 Bishop St. Suite E3 Atlanta, GA 30318
room_description: Your detective unit has been assigned to a scandalous robbery: the world's most expensive diamond called The Siena III was stolen from the British Royal Family! The thief's identity is no secret - he is the untouchable billionaire mastermind Claude Juan Philippe. The diamond is hidden somewhere in his mansion. Claude will be distracted for 60 minutes. Don't let him catch you!
